  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

        - Stable or exacerbating seborrheic dermatitis in the facial area

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Psoriasis

          -  Atopic dermatitis

          -  Facial acne and rosacea

          -  Dermatophytic skin infections

          -  Parkinson's disease

          -  Known immunosuppression; HIV infection

          -  Any condition requiring continuous systemic or topical corticosteroid or antimycotic
             therapy

          -  Continuous asthma inhalation treatment requiring &gt; 800 mg corticosteroids

          -  Any severe disease likely to interfere with the conduct or the planned termination of
             the study
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
